[SN]TITLE[SN]
Kenya looks to avoid oil tax tangles

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Kenya's government wants to reap the benefits of its newly found oil deposits, but also mineral mining.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
15 August 2014 Last updated at 13:27 BST
It wants to take advantage of lucrative licensing deals through capital gains and windfall taxation, but wants to avoid legal wrangling.
The BBC's Anne Soy reports.
